OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to stalking women's
OL,4,Cfootballer
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to stalking
OL,7,FLiverpool FC women's team player Marie
OL,8,FHobinger with inappropriate and
OL,9,Fsexualised messages.
OL,11,FMangal Dalal, 42, from Westminster,
OL,12,FLondon, repeatedly sent messages to
OL,13,FHobinger via Instagram between 27
OL,14,FJanuary and 16 February.
OL,16,FThe messages were often sexually
OL,17,Fexplicit and included his mobile
OL,18,Fnumber and postcode. He asked her to
OL,19,Fvisit him and implied he would come to
OL,20,Ffootball games to see her.
