OL,6,FMs Hobinger became increasingly
OL,7,Fconcerned and blocked him and informed
OL,8,FLiverpool FC.
OL,10,FOn 16 February, Dalal travelled to an
OL,11,FLFC women's team away game in
OL,12,FManchester and waited at the pitch
OL,13,Fside once the game had finished.
OL,15,FA steward at the ground spotted Dalal
OL,16,Fand alerted LFC's safety officer who
OL,17,Fhad started travelling to matches with
OL,18,FMs Hobinger because of concerns for
OL,19,Fher safety.
