OL,6,FDalal was identified as the stalker
OL,7,Fand was later questioned by police
OL,8,Fand, in a prepared statement, admitted
OL,9,Fto the conduct but said that he was
OL,10,Fmentally unwell at the time.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service
OL,13,Fauthorised a charge of stalking and
OL,14,FDalal pleaded guilty at Liverpool
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court, on 4 December.
OL,17,FHe will be sentenced on 20 January
OL,18,F2026 at Westminster Magistrates' Court.
