OL,6,FSenior Crown Prosecutor Sarah
OL,7,FMcInerney said: "Marie Hobinger is a
OL,8,Ftalented professional sportswoman at
OL,9,Fthe top of her game.
OL,11,F"Mangal Dalal targeted her and treated
OL,12,Fher as an object that he could use to
OL,13,Fair his fantasies.
OL,15,F"His messaging was intense, continual,
OL,16,Fand totally inappropriate. It had a
OL,17,Fserious impact on the player who was
OL,18,Fsimply trying to play to the best of
OL,19,Fher ability in a sport and team that
OL,20,Fshe loves.
